name: Tezzy Everydays #7 | Teztopus | May 13th, 2021
description: This is the seventh day of my 1 of 1 pixel art series. Every pixel art piece will involve everyones favorite coin, which most certainly is Tezos.  I went with another quick music video today. In this video, the pixel art octopus is vibrating with colorful excitement as it finally has it's shiny new Tezos coin. Music is "Undersea World" by Clipdad. Tezzy Everydays are created by @clipdad_
